headline: Centene Extends SilverSummit's Presence to the Edges of Nevada
summary: CNC's subsidiary, SilverSummit, secures a five-year Nevada Medicaid contract, reinforcing its foothold in managed care in rural and frontier areas.

headline: 3 Reasons UHS is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Although the S&P 500 is down 9.9% over the past six months, Universal Health Services’s stock price has fallen further to $178.59, losing shareholders 16.7% of their capital. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
